s risk management process is applied during construction of the portfolio the portfolio is fully invested at all times performance supplemental information and disclosures large cap value annual disclosures  kb pdf large cap value performance report  kb pdf our systematic process strategies large cap core equity large cap core international large cap growth equity large cap value equity mid cap growth equity mid cap value equity to be wise stewards of clients capital and relationships home about our firm people careers strategies large cap core equity large cap core international large cap growth equity large cap value equity mid cap growth equity mid cap value equity contact us news   browse home about  strategiescontactnews   strategies large cap corelarge cap core international  large cap growthlarge cap valuemid cap growthmid cap value contact herndon capital management  peachtree street nesuite atlanta ga phone legalcompliance  herndon capital management mid cap value equity fund skip to navigation strategies mid cap value equity mid cap value equity “to everything there is a season” ecclesiastes  true value is defined by companies that trade at a discount to what their fundamentals merit identifying sound companies out of favor with investors due to temporary conditions has historically proven to be a successful strategy as their true value is ultimately recognized in the marketplace we call these companies valuecreating opportunities our process identifies stocks based upon relative value versus the other stocks in our russell mid cap index we combine fundamental analysis in a valuationoriented framework with risk assessment we do not want to own stocks merely because they appear cheap  we screen our value candidates for performancebased characteristics to avoid value traps  the stocks we own tend to have low valuation metrics but they also have sound fundamental characteristics hopefully leading to outperformance as their value is recognized in the market performance supplemental information and disclosures mid cap value annual disclosure  kb pdf mid cap value performance report  kb pdf our systematic process strategies large cap core equity large cap core international large cap growth equity large cap value equity mid cap growth equity mid cap value equity to be wise stewards of clients capital and relationships home about our firm people careers strategies large cap core equity large cap core international large cap growth equity large cap value equity mid cap growth equity mid cap value equity contact us news   browse home about  strategiescontactnews   strategies large cap corelarge cap core international  large cap growthlarge cap valuemid cap growthmid cap value contact herndon capital management  peachtree street nesuite atlanta ga phone legalcompliance  herndon capital management about herndon capital skip to navigation about our firm herndon capital management is an institutional investment management firm specializing in large and mid capitalization equity strategies founded and registered with the sec in  the firm is an affiliate of atlanta life financial group alfg a financial services firm founded in  the firm began managing assets in june  serving a variety of institutional clients hcm has a primary focus of large cap funds these funds serve to help balance the sectors of public pension funds endowments and other institutional assets  history of our name alonzo franklin herndon a former slave founded what is currently atlanta life financial group in  herndon began his successful entrepreneurial track owning and operating a barber shop the only african american business located on historic peachtree street in  also revered for his philanthropic endeavors alonzo herndon became atlanta’s first african american millionaire with a similar drive for business success herndon capital management hcm is proud to share his name carrying on his legacy is an integral part of the culture of herndon capital management 