many years of equity trading experience to hcm he has traded in both domestic and international markets kenny will be responsible for trading all the equity products offered by hcm “the unique skill set antoinette acquired during her tenure on the sell side will prove to be very beneficial to hcm as we remain dedicated to meeting our clients’ needs during this tremendous growth phase of our business” said arlene pine hcm’s director of marketing  client services annette marshall hcm’s chief compliance officer said “we are very excited about the addition of kenny jackson to our trading team he brings extensive experience in trading both domestic and international securities which will complement our existing trading platform and will position us for continued growth in all products” antoinette b scroggins vice president client services antoinette brings  years of experience in the financial services industry to hcm prior to joining the firm antoinette managed the institutional sales and trading desk at boe securities she served as the head trader and was responsible for managing existing client relationships identifying new business opportunities and back office functions prior to joining boe securities inc she worked on the institutional sales and trading desk at the malachi group a boutique investment banking firm where she was responsible for institutional sales and trading operations and compliance antoinette completed her bba in finance from saint joseph’s university she successfully passed the finra licensing exams series    and  kenneth r jackson senior equity trader kenny brings  years of experience in the investment management industry prior to joining hcm he was a principal at qubit investments llc where he helped manage a startup equity market neutral hedge fund which included responsibility for daily trading operations  prior to joining qubit investments kenny spent  years at delaware investments kenny served as an equity quantitative analyst for seven years providing risk management and modeling for large cap value small cap value and core products he also served as a member of the large cap value portfolio construction committee in  kenny joined the equity trading desk executing both domestic and international securities during his tenure as part of the international trading team they ranked  globally vs vwap via the elkins mcsherry global transaction cost analysis  survey kenneth graduated from hampton university with a bachelor of science degree in finance in  about herndon capital management llc hcm founded and registered with the sec in  hcm is an institutional money management firm specializing in us and international large and midcap equity strategies at the end of dec  hcm had approximately  client relationships and close to  billion of assets under management for more information please visit us at wwwherndoncapitalcom or contact arlene pine cfa director of marketing and client services via phone at   or via email at apineherndoncapcom this entry was posted in people moves bookmark the permalink ← can hollywood and chinese investors help wall street from wall street to writer avenue → comments are closed   july  s m t w t f s « oct              streetid twitter feed did bernie madoff run a hedge fund httptcodsxbote via streetid hfpr  wall street pay back near prerecession highs httptcoccnlystq via cnnmoney wallstreet financialindustry  via nprnews ask a banker what do investment bankers actually do httptconuthxi investment  more updates powered by twitter tools  broad street th floor new york ny   infostreetidcom   streetidcom all rights reserved site map home what is streetid news community learn contact us link to us university affiliates media promotions privacy policy terms  conditions   nasdaqcom hot topics etfs  smart portfolio  currencies  online broker center search home  quotes  ownership  insider trades  institutional portfolio no holdings for this institution latest news headlines atos signs cont