ately owned investment manager the firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals it also caters to other individuals investment companies pension and profit sharing plans pooled investment vehicles charitable organizations corporations state or municipal government entities other investment advisers insurance companies foundations and endowments the firm manages separate clientfocused equity portfolios it also manages equity mutual funds the firm invests in the public equity markets across the globe it invests in value and growth stocks of largecap and midcap companies the firm employs a combination of quantita herndon capital management llc is a privately owned investment manager the firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals it also caters to other individuals investment companies pension and profit sharing plans pooled investment vehicles charitable organizations corporations state or municipal government entities other investment advisers insurance companies foundations and endowments the firm manages separate clientfocused equity portfolios it also manages equity mutual funds the firm invests in the public equity markets across the globe it invests in value and growth stocks of largecap and midcap companies the firm employs a combination of quantitative and fundamental analysis with a bottomup stock picking approach to create its portfolios it benchmarks the performance of its equity portfolios against the sp  index russell  index russell  growth index russell  value index russell midcap growth index russell midcap value index msci eafe index and msci acwi ex us index the firm employs a combination of inhouse and external research to make its investments it was formerly known as atlanta life investment advisors inc the firm was founded in  and is based in atlanta georgia herndon capital management llc operates as a subsidiary of atlanta life financial group inc detailed description  peachtree street north eastsuite a